title: DAZ3D - Old Industrial Interior
description:
Old Industrial Interior features an interior scene with a pose-able door that load as a full scene Preload with spool props . (All props are separate items grouped together. So the walls, door, floor, ceiling, and spool props can all be individually selected to move around, or can be hidden for added versatility with camera angles.)
